'''3C48'''是許多[[類星體|類星體]]之中第一顆被發現的。<ref>{{cite journal | last = Weaver | first = Kenneth F. | title = The Incredible Universe | journal = [[National_Geographic|National Geographic]] | issue = Vol. 145 No. 5 | pages = 589–633|date=May 1974}}</ref> 

'''3C 48'''是[[劍橋大學電波星表第三版|劍橋大學電波星表第三版]]中的第一個源，它是由[[Allan_Sandage|Allan Sandage]]和[[Thomas_Matthews|Thomas Matthews]]于1960年通過[[干涉儀|干涉儀]]發現的。<ref>{{cite journal
 | author=Matthews, Thomas A.; Sandage, Allan R.
 | title=Optical Identification of 3c 48, 3c 196, and 3c 286 with Stellar Objects
 | year=1963
 | journal=Astrophysical Journal
 | volume=138
 | pages=30–56
 | url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1963ApJ...138...30M
 | doi=10.1086/147615
 | format=abstract
 | access-date=2008-10-08
 | archive-date=2019-07-12
 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190712185628/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1963ApJ...138...30M
 | dead-url=no
 }}</ref>
[[Jesse_Greenstein|Jesse Greenstein]]和Thomas Matthews發現其[[紅移|紅移]]足足有0.367，是當時所知最高紅移的源之一。<ref>{{cite journal
 | author=Greenstein, J. L.; Matthews, T. A.
 | title=Red-Shift of the Unusual Radio Source 3C48
 | year=1963
 | journal=Nature
 | volume=197
 | pages=1041–1042
 | url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1963Natur.197.1041G
 | doi=10.1038/1971041a0
 | format=abstract
 | access-date=2008-10-08
 | archive-date=2019-07-23
 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190723204306/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1963Natur.197.1041G
 }}</ref>
直到1982年，人們才發現其周圍的一個黯淡星系狀星雲和3C 48有相同的紅移，加固了3C 48位于遙遠星系的理論。<ref>{{cite journal
 | author=Todd A. Boroson & Oke, J. B.
 | title=Detection of the underlying galaxy in the QSO 3C48
 | journal=Nature
 | volume=296
 | pages=397–399
 | url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1982Natur.296..397B
 | format=abstract
 | doi=10.1038/296397a0
 | year=1982
 | access-date=2008-10-08
 | archive-date=2014-07-05
 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140705002129/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1982Natur.296..397B
 | dead-url=no
 }}</ref>3C 48也是第一顆被發現有圍繞著它的、有著相同紅移星系的類星體。

